  "content": "# M2.1 Design: Workspace Model & Devcontainer Demo\n\n## Overview\n\nM2.1 adds the **workspace** concept to Corvia — a purpose-built directory for multi-repo knowledge management — and delivers a **devcontainer-based demo** that showcases Corvia working across multiple repos. The workspace serves three roles: template for users, 1-click demo for evaluators, and the development environment we use to build Corvia M3+.\n\n\n## Architecture\n",
